description: Frontend for Nmap This frontend will help you to download and install Nmap as well as use it. Nmap will help you to discover hosts, protocols, open ports, services and its configuration and vulnerabilities on networks. Supports all known Android architectures: arm, mips and x86. Nmap binaries are transferred using HTTPS by default and are fetched from the following port: https://github.com/kost/nmap-android
